headline: Tracking Lone Pine Capital Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update
summary: Lone Pine Capital's 13F portfolio value increased from $12.33B to $13.41B, with holdings rising from 24 to 29, led by Meta, Amazon, and Vistra Corp. See more.

headline: Agoda Highlights Tokyo as Top Global New Year's Eve Destination
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has announced Tokyo as the most popular destination for New Year's Eve, based on accommodation searches. This marks a shift from last year when Taipei held the top spot. Following Tokyo, the list includes Bangkok, Taipei, Pattaya, and Osaka, showcasing a diverse range of preferences among travelers.
